==Translingual==
===Etymology===
From {{der|mul|grc|ξίφος||sword}} and {{m|grc|οὐρά||tail}}, in reference to the long, slender, stiff tail of the horseshoe crab.
===Proper noun===
{{taxoninfl}}
# {{taxon|order|class|Merostomata|distinguished from all other [[chelicerate]]s by having [[compound eye]]s. The only living [[xiphosuran]]s are the [[horseshoe crab]]s}}
